‚∏ª

1Ô∏è‚É£4Ô∏è‚É£ SDK in NOS

NOS uses SDK to operate switch:
	‚Ä¢	Configure VLANs
	‚Ä¢	Route traffic
	‚Ä¢	Apply ACLs
	‚Ä¢	Monitor counters

NOS = control plane
ASIC SDK = data plane interface

‚∏ª

1Ô∏è‚É£5Ô∏è‚É£ Register Access via SDK

ASIC controlled through registers.

SDK provides functions like:

